title: DEXTER SEASON 9 HAPPENING IN 2021!
author: Reel Talk
comment: Deb is gonna replace Harry as the voice inside Dexter's head

I think Season 5 is very underrated. I love the idea of Dexter helping someone on their crusade for revenge.
I’ve seen a lot of comments from people predicting that Deb will become the new Harry. I like that idea.
I can't believe this is happening I'm so excited. I wonder what will bring Dexter out of hiding..
If they bring dexter back I'm be so HAPPY. Has to have main guy though... Nobody can fill those shoes
description:
Dexter Season 9 is happen in 2021 as a limited series on Showtime! The original showrunner is coming back for the series. Are you excited? I am!
